<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcbdf0a5b-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s44310"><num value="44310">§ 44310.</num><heading> Ending effective date</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idcbdf0a5c-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s44310/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">In General</inline>.—</heading><content>The authority of the Secretary of Transportation to provide insurance and reinsurance under any provision of this chapter other than sections 44302a and 44305 is not effective after <date date="2014-12-11">December 11, 2014</date>.</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idcbdf0a5d-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s44310/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Insurance of United States Government Property</inline>.—</heading><content>The authority of the Secretary of Transportation to provide insurance and reinsurance for a department, agency, or instrumentality of the United States Government under section 44305 is not effective after <date date="2028-09-30">September 30, 2028</date>.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idcbdf0a5e-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/e">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1173">108 Stat. 1173</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/105/85/dA/tX/s1088/a">Pub. L. 105–85, div. A, title X, § 1088(a)</ref>, <date date="1997-11-18">Nov. 18, 1997</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/111/1921">111 Stat. 1921</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/105/137/s5/a">Pub. L. 105–137, § 5(a)</ref>, <date date="1997-12-02">Dec. 2, 1997</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/111/2641">111 Stat. 2641</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/105/277/dC/tI/s110/c/2">Pub. L. 105–277, div. C, title I, § 110(c)(2)</ref>, <date date="1998-10-21">Oct. 21, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/2681-588">112 Stat. 2681–588</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/106/6/s6">Pub. L. 106–6, § 6</ref>, <date date="1999-03-31">Mar. 31, 1999</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/113/10">113 Stat. 10</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/106/31/tVI/s6002/f">Pub. L. 106–31, title VI, § 6002(f)</ref>, <date date="1999-05-21">May 21, 1999</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/113/113">113 Stat. 113</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/106/181/tVII/s711">Pub. L. 106–181, title VII, § 711</ref>, <date date="2000-04-05">Apr. 5, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/160">114 Stat. 160</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/108/11/tIV/s4001/c">Pub. L. 108–11, title IV, § 4001(c)</ref>, <date date="2003-04-16">Apr. 16, 2003</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/117/606">117 Stat. 606</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/108/176/tI/s106/d">Pub. L. 108–176, title I, § 106(d)</ref>, <date date="2003-12-12">Dec. 12, 2003</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/117/2499">117 Stat. 2499</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/110/181/dA/tIII/s378">Pub. L. 110–181, div. A, title III, § 378</ref>, <date date="2008-01-28">Jan. 28, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/85">122 Stat. 85</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/113/46/dA/s154">Pub. L. 113–46, div. A, § 154</ref>, <date date="2013-10-17">Oct. 17, 2013</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/127/565">127 Stat. 565</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/113/66/dA/tX/